request.description:
It creates a new company.

Schema :  

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "name": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Company name"
    },
    "address": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Full address of the company"
    },
    "contactNo": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Contact number including country code"
    },
    "registeredEmail": {
      "type": "string",
      "format": "email",
      "description": "Registered email of the company"
    }
  },
  "required": ["name", "address", "contactNo", "registeredEmail"]
}


 ```

Creates a new warehouse.

Schema:

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "name": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Name of the warehouse"
    },
    "companyId": {
      "type": "string",
      "format": "uuid",
      "description": "ID of the company this warehouse belongs to"
    }
  },
  "required": ["name", "companyId"]
}


 ```

Adds new product to a company with unique SKU.

Schema:

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "companyId": {
      "type": "string",
      "format": "uuid",
      "description": "ID of the company that owns this product"
    },
    "supplierId": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "string",
        "format": "uuid"
      },
      "description": "List of supplier IDs associated with this product"
    },
    "sku": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Unique Stock Keeping Unit identifier for the product"
    },
    "price": {
      "type": "number",
      "description": "Price of the product"
    },
    "name": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Name of the product"
    },
    "description": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Detailed description of the product"
    }
  },
  "required": ["companyId", "supplierId", "sku", "price", "name"]
}


 ```

Adds new product to inventory.

Schema:

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "productId": {
      "type": "string",
      "format": "uuid",
      "description": "Unique ID of the product"
    },
    "warehouseId": {
      "type": "string",
      "format": "uuid",
      "description": "Unique ID of the warehouse where stock is held"
    },
    "quantity": {
      "type": "integer",
      "description": "Number of items to add or update in stock"
    },
    "threshold": {
      "type": "integer",
      "description": "Minimum threshold quantity for alerting low stock"
    },
    "changeType": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Type of stock change (e.g., INITIAL_STOCK, RESTOCK, SALE)"
    },
    "note": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Optional note about the stock change"
    }
  },
  "required": ["productId", "warehouseId", "quantity", "threshold", "changeType"]
}


 ```

Updates the Inventory.

Schema:

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "id": {
      "type": "string",
      "format": "uuid",
      "description": "Unique ID of the inventory record"
    },
    "quantity": {
      "type": "integer",
      "description": "Updated quantity of the product"
    },
    "threshold": {
      "type": "integer",
      "description": "Minimum threshold quantity for alerting low stock"
    },
    "changeType": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Type of stock change (e.g., SOLD, RESTOCK, RETURN)"
    },
    "note": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Optional note about the stock change"
    }
  },
  "required": ["id", "quantity", "threshold", "changeType"]
}


 ```
